:name: XIAO RP2040 Motor Encoder PID
:description: This script runs the Motor PID Encoder example on the Seeed XIAO RP2040.

$name?="XIAO-RP2040"

using sysbus
mach create $name

machine LoadPlatformDescription @examples/motor_pid_encoder/motor_encoder.repl

$bin?=@.pio/build/seeed-xiao-rp2040/firmware.elf

showAnalyzer sysbus.uart0

macro reset
"""
    sysbus LoadELF $bin
"""

runMacro $reset
